Wrap text by width

# Note

- This macro process width as unicode width

# Arguments

- a_width : A width(chars) of given texts ( trimmed )
- a_text  : Text to wrap

# Demo

```
$wrap(20,$lipsum(10))
===
Lorem ipsum dolor
sit amet consectetur
adipiscing elit. In
rhoncus
```

# Example

$assert(\\*Lorem ipsum
dolor sit amet,
consectetur
adipiscing elit. In
rhoncus*\\,$wrap(20,$lipsum(10)))
